SITUATION: 30-year-old G1P0 with dichorionic diamniotic twin pregnancy at 32+2 weeks presenting with preterm labor and growth discordance

BACKGROUND: Mrs Liu conceived via IVF after 2 years of unexplained infertility, single embryo transfer resulted in spontaneous splitting to monozygotic twins. Pregnancy has been closely monitored with fortnightly scans.
